---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="EU Compliance" description="Integrated EU AI Act, MDR, IVDR, and GDPR advisory. Risk classification, technical documentation review, and compliance roadmaps for companies that need to get regulation right.">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">EU Compliance</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">EU AI Act, MDR, IVDR, and GDPR advisory for companies that need to get regulation right.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        Companies deploying AI in regulated sectors face overlapping
        obligations. The EU AI Act covers high-risk AI systems across
        healthcare, finance, hiring, and critical infrastructure.
        Sector-specific rules like MDR and IVDR apply to medical AI. GDPR
        governs every system that touches personal data. Treating these as
        separate projects leads to duplicated documentation, missed
        dependencies, and longer time to market.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-4">
        AnichLabs OÜ delivers integrated EU regulatory advisory. We map
        your product against the EU AI Act, sector-specific rules, and
        GDPR requirements together, identify the dependencies, and produce
        a single compliance roadmap. Engineering depth, domain judgement,
        and regulatory expertise in one engagement.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">What we deliver</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:shield-check" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">EU AI Act Risk Classification</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Formal assessment of your AI system's risk level (minimal, limited, high-risk, or prohibited) with written justification under Annex III.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:file-alt" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">MDR / IVDR Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Review and gap analysis of your technical documentation against MDR Annex II/III and IVDR requirements, including conformity assessment routes for medical devices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:lock" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">GDPR Advisory</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">DPIAs for high-risk processing, processing records, and Article 9 compliance for special category data including health, biometric, and behavioural information.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:map" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Integrated Compliance Roadmap</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">A single written roadmap mapping your gaps across all relevant regulations to prioritised actions, timelines, and resource estimates.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Is my AI system automatically high-risk under the EU AI Act?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">High-risk classification under Annex III applies to AI used in medical devices, recruitment, credit scoring, education, law enforcement, and other listed domains. Whether your specific system qualifies depends on its function and context, which is part of what we assess.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Do you act as our EU Authorised Representative or Article 27 GDPR representative?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Not directly today. We provide regulatory advisory and prepare your documentation, then connect you with vetted AR and Article 27 partners where needed. Direct services from AnichLabs are planned for 2027.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            How long does compliance take?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">A gap analysis and integrated roadmap takes 3 to 6 weeks. Achieving full compliance depends on your starting point, typically 3 to 12 months for a high-risk system.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-16 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Need an EU compliance roadmap?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call to confirm your regulatory scope and what compliance requires.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>
